    "body": "You know I was thinking about this, and I had an idea that kind of works like a tax credit...but the details are where this will be very hard to implement. If Suicide is written into the opcodes near the end of the codes, you get something like a tax credit on the amount of gas it would cost in terms of your opcode because you're alleviating storage costs. Again, the devil is in the details on this one. \n",
